            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>enio</ex></expan> |(centuriae) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> P<expan><ex>hi</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ippianae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Flavianus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>opt</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> in <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>com</abbr><ex>manipularium</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> P<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>il</abbr><ex>ippo</ex></expan> et Titiano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift befindet sich auf dem Sockel der Statuette eines Genius im Hüftmantel mit Füllhorn. Zeile 3: IN-Ligatur; Zeile 4: IMP-, ET- Ligatur. Material nach Kremer: Hell gelblicher Marmor, mit hellgrauen und goldgelben Verfärbungen. (B): Bormann: Z. 1: P(i)l(ippianae); Z. 4: Pil(ippo).</p>
            </div>
